<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<meta name="description" content="Mariage de Marie et Robin" />
		<title>Marie & Robin - Mariage</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,400&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
	</head>
	<body>
		<main>
			<section class="bento hero">
				<div class="hero-content">
					<p class="save-the-date">SAVE THE DATE</p>
					<h1>Marie <span class="amp">&</span> Robin</h1>
					<p class="date">20 Juin 2026</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="bento couple">
				<div class="bento-header">
					<h2>Les Mariés</h2>
				</div>
				<p>Nous avons décisidé de nous engager l'un envers l'autre et nous voulons celebrate notre amour avec vous, nos proches.</p>
			</section>

			<section class="bento lieu">
				<div class="bento-header">
					<h2>Le Lieu</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="lieu-details">
					<div class="lieu-item">
						<h3>La Cérémonie</h3>
						<p class="adresse">Mairie de Saint-Émilion</p>
						<p>Place du Clocher</p>
						<p>33330 Saint-Émilion</p>
					</div>
					<div class="lieu-item">
						<h3>La Réception</h3>
						<p class="adresse">Château de la Mer</p>
						<p>Route des Vignes</p>
						<p>33330 Saint-Émilion</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="bento horaire">
				<div class="bento-header">
					<h2>Horário</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">14h30</span>
						<span class="event">Cérémonie civile</span>
					</div>
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">16h00</span>
						<span class="event">Vin d'honneur</span>
					</div>
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">18h00</span>
						<span class="event">Photos de groupe</span>
					</div>
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">19h00</span>
						<span class="event">Entrée des mariés</span>
					</div>
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">20h00</span>
						<span class="event">Dîner</span>
					</div>
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">22h30</span>
						<span class="event">Premier dance</span>
					</div>
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<span class="time">23h30</span>
						<span class="event">Suite des festivités</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="bento gift">
				<div class="bento-header">
					<h2>Liste de Mariage</h2>
				</div>
				<p>Votre présence est le plus beau des cadeaux. Cependant, si vous souhaitez nous offrir quelque chose, nous avons prévu une liste.</p>
				<a href="#" class="btn">Voir la liste</a>
			</section>

			<section class="bento rsvp">
				<div class="bento-header">
					<h2>RSVP</h2>
				</div>
				<p>Merci de confirmer votre présence avant le <strong>15 Mai 2026</strong></p>
				<a href="mailto:marie.et.robin@email.com" class="btn">Répondre par email</a>
			</section>

			<section class="bento contact">
				<div class="bento-header">
					<h2>Contact</h2>
				</div>
				<p>Pour toute question, n'hésitez pas à nous contacter.</p>
				<div class="contact-info">
					<p><strong>Marie:</strong> 06 XX XX XX XX</p>
					<p><strong>Robin:</strong> 06 XX XX XX XX</p>
					<p><a href="mailto:marie.et.robin@email.com">marie.et.robin@email.com</a></p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="bento info">
				<div class="bento-header">
					<h2>Infos Pratiques</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="info-grid">
					<div class="info-item">
						<h3>Hébergement</h3>
						<p>Plusieurs hôtels et gîtes sont disponibles à Saint-Émilion. Nous vous recommandons de réserver tôt!</p>
					</div>
					<div class="info-item">
						<h3>Parking</h3>
						<p>Un parking gratuit est disponible sur place.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="info-item">
						<h3>Tenues</h3>
						<p>Tenue elegante demandée. Couleurs: bleu, vert, beige.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="info-item">
						<h3>Enfants</h3>
						<p>Les enfants sont les bienvenus. Un service de garde sera organisé pendant le dîner.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<footer class="footer">
				<p>Merci de célébrer avec nous ce jour spécial!</p>
				<p class="love">Marie & Robin</p>
			</footer>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>

<style is:global>
	:root {
		--off-white: #F9F7F3;
		--off-white-dark: #EDE9E0;
		--hydrangea: #7BA3C9;
		--hydrangea-light: #A8C5DB;
		--green: #6B8E5A;
		--green-light: #8BA87A;
		--text: #3D3D3D;
		--text-light: #6B6B6B;
	}

	* {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	html {
		font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
		background: var(--off-white);
		color: var(--text);
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}

	body {
		min-height: 100vh;
		background: 
			radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(123, 163, 201, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
			radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(107, 142, 90, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%),
			var(--off-white);
	}

	main {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 2rem 1rem;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.bento {
		background: white;
		border-radius: 1.5rem;
		padding: 2rem;
		box-shadow: 
			0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04),
			0 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.bento:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 
			0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06),
			0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
	}

	.bento-header h2 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--hydrangea);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--hydrangea-light);
		display: inline-block;
	}

	.hero {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 4rem 2rem;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--hydrangea-light) 0%, white 50%, var(--green-light) 100%);
	}

	.hero .save-the-date {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.3em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--text-light);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.hero h1 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.hero .amp {
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--hydrangea);
	}

	.hero .date {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--green);
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.couple {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
		text-align: center;
		background: transparent;
		box-shadow: none;
		padding: 1rem 2rem;
	}

	.couple p {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--text-light);
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.lieu {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	.lieu-details {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.lieu-item h3 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		color: var(--green);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.lieu-item .adresse {
		font-weight: 500;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.lieu-item p {
		color: var(--text-light);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.horaire {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	.timeline {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(140px, 1fr));
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.timeline-item {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 1rem;
		background: var(--off-white);
		border-radius: 1rem;
	}

	.timeline-item .time {
		font-weight: 500;
		color: var(--hydrangea);
		font-size: 1.1rem;
	}

	.timeline-item .event {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
		margin-top: 0.25rem;
	}

	.gift {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
		text-align: center;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, white 0%, var(--off-white) 100%);
	}

	.gift p {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.rsvp {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.rsvp p {
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.rsvp strong {
		color: var(--hydrangea);
	}

	.contact {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	.contact-info {
		margin-top: 1rem;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.contact-info p {
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.contact-info a {
		color: var(--hydrangea);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.contact-info a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}

	.info {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
	}

	.info-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
	}

	.info-item h3 {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: var(--green);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.info-item p {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.btn {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
		background: var(--hydrangea);
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 3rem;
		font-weight: 500;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.btn:hover {
		background: var(--green);
		transform: scale(1.02);
	}

	.footer {
		grid-column: 1 / -1;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 3rem 2rem;
		color: var(--text-light);
	}

	.footer .love {
		font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		color: var(--hydrangea);
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		main {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}

		.hero h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
		}

		.hero {
			padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
		}

		.timeline {
			grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
		}
	}
</style>
